  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">420 food packs to be distributed to affected families in Brgy Bagong Silang, Puerto Princesa City, Province of Palawan, Philippines</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Over 400 families were affected by the large fire in Barangay Bagong Silang, a coastal village in Puerto Princesa City, Palawan Province

420 houses are damaged; 395 homes destroyed; 1,642 people displaced

Affected families are now staying in 1 evacuation center at the barangay center.

The affected families are likely to stay in the evacuation center up to a month or more. A new relocation area for the affected families is already identified as the local government does not allow the affected families to reconstruct their houses in the same location due to fire hazard.</narrative>
  </description>
